query:
SELECT om.id, om.omUserId, om.omOrgId, om.omRole, u.name, u.email, u.platform_owner, o.name as org_name, o.account_id
FROM org_memberships om
JOIN users u ON u.id = om.omUserId
JOIN organizations o ON o.id = om.omOrgId
WHERE u.name LIKE '%Junaid%' OR u.email LIKE '%junaid%'
